snippet.title: A SKETCH basic javascript graph user plug-in
snippet.description: The vector graph application Sketch for Mac lets you develop your own plug-ins which makes it easy to automate tasks inside the vector graph application. This should make the path for many plug-ins, as many brilliant javascript developer exists around the globe. You can find the example simple plug-in here: https://gist.github.com/netsi1964/523a837385f0488498678a6fb5ea3ba2
